reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good value, but still have warning light
reviews.reviewText: I think this was a much less expensive option than offered by ADT and it seemed to replace the old one just fine. It was a bit hard to get the old one out, but this one connected easily and fit perfectly in the old one's space. The light for "weak battery" is still on (which is possibly an ADT issue), but the panel is no longer beeping at weird hours of the night so I am happy.
